{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/dawn-theme-add-a-read-more-button-to-the-product-page","result":{"pageContext":{"id":1400,"date":"2022-01-28T20:18:30","date_gmt":"2022-01-28T20:18:30","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=1400"},"modified":"2022-01-29T03:15:09","modified_gmt":"2022-01-29T03:15:09","slug":"dawn-theme-add-a-read-more-button-to-the-product-page","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/dawn-theme-add-a-read-more-button-to-the-product-page/","title":{"rendered":"Dawn theme: add a &#8220;Read More&#8221; button to the product page"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>When you are announcing products that require descriptions that are rich in details, they can end up adding a large wall of text to your product page which, very likely, will end up scaring your potential customers  away.<br><br>A common solution for this type of problem is adding a &#8220;read more&#8221; type of button. Although there are apps that will enable this functionality for you, they ship tied up with monthly fees and a lot of bloat coded that will end up slowing down your store&#8217;s website. <br><br>In this tutorial I&#8217;ll show you how you can easily add that by simply pasting a piece of code to your Dawn theme.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Downloading the code files</h3>\n\n\n\n<p> You can download the code files <a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/shop/dawn-theme-read-more\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">clicking here</a>. (<a href=\"https://pandashopdeals.myshopify.com/products/bedside-table\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">live preview</a>)<br><br>Complete details about it can be found <a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/shop/dawn-theme-read-more\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">here</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Making a backup of your theme</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Before diving into the tutorial make sure you download the theme, so in case you face any issues you can easily revert back.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1514\" height=\"481\" class=\"wp-image-503\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png 1514w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-600x191.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-1200x381.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-768x244.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1514px) 100vw, 1514px\" /></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-step-1-opening-the-code-editor\">Step 1: opening the code editor</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>In your Shopify admin, go to <strong>Online Store</strong> > <strong>Themes </strong>> <strong>Actions </strong>> <strong>Edit Code</strong>.</li><li>Inside the <a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/shop/dawn-theme-read-more\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">.zip you downloaded</a> you&#8217;ll find two files: <ol><li><strong>ezfy-read-more.txt</strong></li><li><strong>settings_schema.txt</strong></li></ol></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3>Step 1: creating the code snippet</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Open the <strong>ezfy-read-more.txt </strong>file and copy all the code in there.</li><li>Now go back to your Shopify code editor and below <strong>Snippets</strong> click on &#8220;<em>Add a new snippet</em>&#8220;. <br><br>Name it exactly: <strong>ezfy-read-more</strong><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1918\" height=\"699\" class=\"wp-image-602\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/newsnip.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/newsnip.png 1918w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/newsnip-600x219.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/newsnip-1200x437.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/newsnip-768x280.png 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/newsnip-1536x560.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1918px) 100vw, 1918px\" /><br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1657\" height=\"806\" class=\"wp-image-604\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/create.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/create.jpg 1657w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/create-600x292.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/create-1200x584.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/create-768x374.jpg 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/create-1536x747.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1657px) 100vw, 1657px\" /></li><li>Paste the code that you copied and click on <strong>save</strong>.<br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1904\" height=\"879\" class=\"wp-image-606\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/save1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/save1.jpg 1904w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/save1-600x277.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/save1-1200x554.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/save1-768x355.jpg 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/save1-1536x709.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1904px) 100vw, 1904px\" /></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3>Step 2: adding the code snippet to the product page</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Find the file named <strong>theme.liquid</strong>.</li><li>Inside this file, press CTRL + F (or CMD + F on Mac) and search for:<br><br><strong>&lt;/body&gt;</strong></li><li>Paste the following code <strong>before </strong>the <strong>&lt;/body&gt;</strong> tag you found:<br><br><pre>{% include 'ezfy-read-more' %}</pre><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1542\" height=\"757\" class=\"wp-image-608\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/bdy.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/bdy.jpg 1542w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/bdy-600x295.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/bdy-1200x589.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/bdy-768x377.jpg 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/bdy-1536x754.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1542px) 100vw, 1542px\" /></li><li>Click on save.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-4th-and-final-step-updating-the-settings_schema-txt-file\">4th and final step: updating the settings_schema.txt file </h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Open the <strong>settings_schema.txt </strong>file and copy all the code in there.</li><li>In your Shopify code editor find the <strong>settings_schema.json</strong> file in your theme.</li><li>Scroll all the way down.</li><li>Paste the code<strong> before</strong> the last line, after the <strong>} </strong>sign, as indicated the image below.<br><br>So, for example, in this case, the code should be pasted on the line <strong>351 </strong>(the quantity of lines may vary depending of your theme, so don&#8217;t worry if it shows a different number on yours).<br> </li></ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"649\" height=\"694\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/image-3.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1373\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Paste the code to the right of the <strong>}</strong> character that the arrow is pointing to.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"681\" height=\"684\" class=\"wp-image-1375\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/ez2.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/ez2.jpg 681w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/ez2-200x200.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 681px) 100vw, 681px\" /><br></li><li>Save and you&#8217;re ready to go!</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-troubleshooting-common-issues\">Troubleshooting common issues</h3>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Question</strong>: It shows me an error after I edit the <strong>settings_schema.json</strong> file. What do I do?</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1023\" height=\"755\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/error1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-522\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/error1.jpg 1023w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/error1-600x443.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/error1-768x567.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1023px) 100vw, 1023px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Answer</strong>: You very likely pasted the code at the bottom of the file. Please make sure you paste the code at the penultimate (second last) line as indicated in <strong>step 4</strong>.<br><br>Your file must end with this character: <strong>]</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you&#8217;re still facing any issues please reach out to us via <strong>ezfycode@gmail.com</strong> and we&#8217;ll be more than happy to help you out!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-customizing-the-read-more-looks-and-feels\">Customizing the &#8220;read more&#8221; looks and feels </h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>On the top right of the theme you&#8217;re editing, click on &#8220;Customize theme&#8221;.<br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1021\" height=\"549\" class=\"wp-image-1403\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/c1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/c1.jpg 1021w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/c1-850x457.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/c1-768x413.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1021px) 100vw, 1021px\" /><br>2. Click on &#8220;theme settings&#8221;, at the bottom.<br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"606\" height=\"324\" class=\"wp-image-1405\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/c2.jpg\" alt=\"\"><br>3. Now click on &#8220;EZFY Read More&#8221; and you can customize it as per your wish.<br></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/dOCzDkbrl1j2hSgbCY/giphy.gif\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have any issues or questions just reach out to us at <strong>ezfycode@gmail.com</strong> and we&#8217;ll be very happy to help you!</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-container-621da9a9a5032 wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"></div></div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Effortlessly add a &#8220;read more&#8221; button to the description of your Dawn theme product pages.</p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1418,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[9],"tags":[154,435,82],"image_alt":"","acf":[],"featured_image_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/dawn_read_more-1-850x478.jpg","featured_image_small_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/dawn_read_more-1-200x200.jpg","featured_image_large_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/dawn_read_more-1-1200x675.jpg","post_count":null,"categories_names":["Blog"],"tag_names":["Code Tutorial","Dawn Theme","product page"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1400"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/users/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/comments?post=1400"}],"version-history":[{"count":8,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1400/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1425,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1400/revisions/1425"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media/1418"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media?parent=1400"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https://www